cast.name: 费利克斯·伦耶尔 Félix Lengyel
小达伦·贾森·沃特金斯 Darren Jason Watkins Jr.

introduction: The Sidemen, an English based YouTube group created over a decade ago between a group of friends, battle it out in the world's game against a number of other popular social media and streaming legends. On a large field, after years of intense training, we will find out who wins the trophy and takes home the title of champion. But, there are certainly some reasons to tune in. Many unknowns. Will Ishowspeed kick the goal he has always wanted to? Will Steventries make someone cry? And will Ethan manage to get his dick sucked from the goal he scores? Find it all out, by watching the Sidemen Charity match.
